# Kartal package

This repo ships **kartal**, Flutter extensions on `BuildContext`, `String`, `Future`, collections, and small utilities.

- Human docs: root `README.md`.
- Agent-focused rules: `ai/cursor/*.mdc` (this file + scoped Dart rules).
- Claude skills: `ai/claude/*/SKILL.md`.

When editing **user apps** that depend on kartal, prefer kartal APIs from those rules instead of reintroducing verbose `MediaQuery` / `Navigator` / `FutureBuilder` boilerplate—unless a scoped rule or `kartal-do-not-overuse` says otherwise.

Do **not** modify generated Dart (`*.g.dart`, `*.freezed.dart`, …).
